				<p sameAs="title">Private letter from Manuel Rodrigues de Carvalho, knight of the order of Santiago, to António Rodrigues Gorelho, notary.</p>
				<p sameAs="summary">The author conveys his opinion regarding the sale of a certain dwelling, bequeathed by a deceased, authorizing that its auctioning to be fulfilled.</p>
				<p sameAs="settingDesc">The letters included in this case relate to the part of the inheritance of the deceased Catherine de Moura de Bettencourt allegedly received by her executor, Manuel Rodrigues de Carvalho.</p>
